@startuml
title Sequence Diagram (Pipeline Completa con Web Search) - Iterazione 4

actor Utente                         as U
participant "Browser\n(React App)"   as FE
participant "API Gateway\n(FastAPI)"  as GW
participant "Orchestrator Agent"      as Orch
participant "Classifier Agent"        as Cls
participant "Query Agent"             as QA
participant "Web Agent\n(Tavily)"     as WA
participant "Generator Agent"         as Gen
participant "Revision Agent"          as Rev
participant "Pipeline Logger"         as Log
participant "File System\n(logs/)"    as FS

' ─── 1. Invio query con history ──────────────────────────────
U   -> FE   : Inserisce domanda
FE  -> FE   : Costruisce conversation_history\n(ultimi 10 messaggi)
FE  -> GW   : POST /api/agent/query\n[Cookie: access_token=<JWT>]\n{ query, user_info, conversation_history }

' ─── 2. Inizializzazione stato ────────────────────────────────
GW  -> Orch : process_query(query, user_info, conversation_history)
Orch -> Orch : Inizializza AgentState\n(query + profilo + history)

' ─── 3. Classificazione ───────────────────────────────────────
Orch -> Cls  : classify(query, user_context, conversation_history)
note right of Cls
  Usa Gemini 2.5 Flash
  per classificare l'intento
end note
Cls  --> Orch : { category, description, confidence }

' ─── 4. Generazione search query ──────────────────────────────
Orch -> QA   : generate_query(query, conversation_history, user_context)
note right of QA
  Usa Gemini 2.5 Flash.
  Decide autonomamente se inserire
  info profilo nella query.
  Restituisce max 6-8 keywords.
end note
QA   --> Orch : { search_query: "parole chiave ottimizzate" }

' ─── 5. Ricerca web ───────────────────────────────────────────
Orch -> WA   : search(search_query)
WA   -> WA   : Tavily.search(query,\ninclude_domains=[unibg.it,\ncoursecatalogue],\nmax_results=30)
WA   -> WA   : Ordina per score, seleziona top 5

alt Risultato è PDF
  WA -> WA   : _extract_pdf_links(url)\ntramite PyMuPDF
end

WA   -> WA   : _format_results(top_results)
WA   --> Orch : { web_results, formatted_context, total_results, status }

' ─── 6. Generazione risposta ─────────────────────────────────
Orch -> Gen  : generate(query, category,\ncontext+web_context,\nuser_context, conversation_history)
note right of Gen
  web_context iniettato in
  context["additional_info"]
  come fonte per la risposta
end note
Gen  --> Orch : { response, status }

' ─── 7. Revisione ────────────────────────────────────────────
Orch -> Rev  : revise(query, draft, category,\nuser_context, conversation_history)
Rev  --> Orch : { revised_response, has_changes }

' ─── 8. Logging pipeline ─────────────────────────────────────
Orch -> Log  : write_log(state, workflow_steps)
Log  -> Log  : _build_filename(matricola, timestamp)
note right of Log
  Nome: log_{matricola}_{timestamp}.txt
  Contiene: header, user info,
  query originale, history,
  step classificatore, query agent,
  web agent, generator, reviser
end note
Log  -> FS   : scrive file log txt
FS   --> Log : filepath
Log  --> Orch : filepath

' ─── 9. Risposta finale ───────────────────────────────────────
Orch --> GW  : { response, category, metadata }
GW   --> FE  : { response, category, metadata }

FE   -> FE   : Aggiunge messaggio alla UI
FE   -> FE   : Salva conversazione in localStorage
FE   --> U   : Visualizza risposta

@enduml
